This paper deals with the extraction of clinical features from unstructured clinical narratives using machine learning and statistical approaches. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the analysis of large datasets, which could fall under the categories of Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper deals with medical data, which could also fall under the category of Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
